<SLUG> BC-FEATURES-BJT08-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    COX NEWS SERVICE FEATURES BUDGET
 &HT;    c. 2000 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   These feature stories are moving today to clients of the New
York Times News Service. Stories are for release Friday, September
8, 2000, unless otherwise embargoed.
</P>
<P>
   LIFESTYLE
</P>
<P>
   YACHT-TRUMPY _ Say 'Trumpy' to a yachtsman, and you may as well
say 'perfection.' Though some of the remaining 90 boats are
derelicts, once they're restored, their wood is as good as gold.
(Reid, Palm Beach Post) WITH ART
</P>
