   SCI-CANCER-DRUG (Undated) _ A Dutch study shows that the risk of
dying from endometrial cancer may be much higher than once thought
for women taking tamoxifen for breast cancer, but some researchers
in the United States disagree because more rigorous studies have
found the opposite. By Denise Grady.
