<HEADLINE>
TOO MANY FLAVORS, TOO MANY INGREDIENTS
</HEADLINE>
  (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
 By ROBERT PHILPOT 
 c.2000 Fort Worth Star-Telegram 
<TEXT>
<P>
   Dwayne, the hero of this ultra-indie movie, is suffering a bit
