<HEADLINE>
TIMOR TRAGEDY OVERSHADOWS U.N.'S MILLENNIUM SUMMIT  
 &HT;   
</HEADLINE>
  
 (ATTN: Commentary Editors)   (This 1,050-word ``separate-buy'' article is from THE INDEPENDENT
newspaper in London.)  
 &HT;    
 (EDITORS: We regret that this material is NOT available to clients
in Canada EXCEPT to The Hamilton (Ontario) Spectator.)  
