<HEADLINE>
INCREASE THE VAMP-OR-TRAMP ELEMENTS WITH FALL ADD-ONS 
WITH PHOTO
</HEADLINE>
  
 (For use by New York Times News Service clients)  c. 2000 Houston Chronicle 
The quickest ways to add vamp power to fall's ladylike looks is
with strong color and cutting-edge accessories.
<TEXT>
<P>
   Pinks, purples and fuchsias are accessory colors that can switch
easily from sensual to sexy. Lily Scott's pink beaded bracelet bag,
$235 at Saks, adds a kittenish touch to a Johnny Was python-print
chiffon blouse, $120 at Dillard's. A Mimo hot pink pashmina with
beaded fringe, $250, and a spangled pink Democracy Weekend
sleeveless sweater, $122, add warmth for fall. Both at Cotton Club.
</P>
<P>
   Color in shoes taps into a more playful mood for fall fashion
fun. Both Prada's lavender and purple leather mules, $370 at Saks,
and Enzo Angiolini's whip-stitched purple python and suede loafers,
$69 at Dillard's, may be worn day or night.
</P>
