   LEFTEYE-MISSING _ Today the New York Post's gossip Page 6
reported that Lisa ``Left Eye'' Lopes of Atlanta trio TLC is
missing. This from the group's publicist, Matt Shelton, who was
expecting her at a press conference this past Tuesday in Las Vegas.
We talk to Shelton and her Atlanta-based business partner/ friend
of 10 years Ian Burke _ who hasn't called the authorities. In fact,
right now he's thinking the friend he hasn't seen since the start
of the Labor Day weekend ``is just somewhere being Lisa Lopes.''
Which we explain as well. (SoMurray, Atlanta Journal-Constitution)
